<h1 class="western">Ideas</h1>
<p>2021-10-04</p>
<ul>
	<li/>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0in">Group is sponsored to enter the
	lower (regional) leagues in the Games Of Lore. Pick an event:</p>
	<ul>
		<li/>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0in">Chase the Sun - a violent
		chariot race in the rocky desert.</p>
		<li/>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0in">Touch the Moon - use catapults
		to launch yourself as high as you can.</p>
		<li/>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0in">Battle to The Last - battle
		event. Can be a tourney or a battle royale.</p>
		<li/>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0in">Grapple the Great Serpent -
		Boat race, involves deadly rapids and waterfalls.&nbsp;</p>
	</ul>
	<li/>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0in">Each team gets a scry beacon
	(magic item, invest) which allows the event to be viewed remotely.</p>
	<li/>
<p>Event areas are selected by military strategy. Various
	hostile factions near the city, and contestants need to be strong &amp;
	aggressive. These events double as &quot;preventative invasions&quot;
	against these hostile neighbors. This kingdom doesn't maintain a
	large army, as there are dozens of adventurer teams. The king and
	local lords employ the most powerful and dangerous people, and are
	themselves high level characters (meritocracy through daring).</p>
</ul>
