<h2 class="western">Event: Battle to The Last</h2>
<ul>
	<li/>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0in">Training and battle. Level up
	fast, get strong, win in the big arena event.</p>
	<ul>
		<li/>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0in">To ensure reliable combat, best
		to do underground fighting to level up</p>
		<li/>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0in">Subterfuge is to learn about
		enemies and equip yourself to exploit weaknesses. Fighting &quot;dirty&quot;
		is common and even applauded... this is a land of Chaos.</p>
		<li/>
<p>Victory is critical, but those who show respect (help them
		up, heal and/or praise defeated opponents) earn much more praise &amp;
		favor... remember this is a land of Good.</p>
	</ul>
</ul>
